
  <sn><md>### Weathering of Pyroxene Family

When the minerals of the pyroxene family are acted upon by `carbonation and hydration`, new minerals, compounds of minerals, and compounds of $\mathrm{Fe}$, $\mathrm{Al}$, $\mathrm{Mg}$, and $\mathrm{Ca}$ are formed.
</md></sn>
